{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a001", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| SRLAT | Laterality | Char | (LAT) | Variable Qualifier | Qualifier for anatomical location further detailing laterality of intervention administration. Examples: \"RIGHT\", \"LEFT\", \"BILATERAL\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a002", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| SRMETHOD | Method of Test or Examination | Char | (METHOD) | Record Qualifier | Method of test or examination. Examples: \"ELISA\", \"EIA\", \"MICRONEUTRALIZATION ASSAY\", \"PLAQUE REDUCTION NEUTRALIZATION ASSAY\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a003", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| SRLOBXFL | Last Observation Before Exposure Flag | Char | (NY) | Record Qualifier | Operationally derived indicator used to identify the last non-missing value prior to RFXSTDTC. The value should be \"Y\" or null. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a004", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| SRBLFL | Baseline Flag | Char | (NY) | Record Qualifier | Indicator used to identify a baseline value. The value should be \"Y\" or null. Note that SRBLFL is retained for backward compatibility. The authoritative baseline flag for statistical analysis is in an ADaM dataset. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a005", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| SREVAL | Evaluator | Char | (EVAL) | Record Qualifier | Role of person who provided evaluation. Used only for results that are subjective (e.g., assigned by a person or a group). Should be null for records that contain collected or derived data. Examples: \"INVESTIGATOR\", \"ADJUDICATION COMMITTEE\", \"VENDOR\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a006", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| VISITNUM | Visit Number | Num | | Timing | Clinical encounter number. Numeric version of VISIT, used for sorting. | Exp |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a007", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| VISIT | Visit Name | Char | | Timing | Protocol-defined description of clinical encounter. May be used in addition to VISITNUM and/or VISITDY. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a008", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| VISITDY | Planned Study Day of Visit | Num | | Timing | Planned study day of the visit based upon RFSTDTC in Demographics. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a009", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| TAETORD | Planned Order of Element within Arm | Num | | Timing | Number that gives the planned order of the element within the arm. | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
{"atom_id": "ig34_p0377_a010", "source": "SDTMIG_v3.4", "page": 377, "page_region": "top", "parent_section": "SR – Specification", "atom_type": "TABLE_ROW", "verbatim": "| EPOCH | Epoch | Char | (EPOCH) | Timing | Epoch associated with the date/time of the observation. Examples: \"SCREENING\", \"TREATMENT\", and \"FOLLOW-UP\". | Perm |", "heading_level": null, "sibling_index": null, "figure_ref": null, "cross_refs": [], "extracted_by": {"subagent_type": "oh-my-claudecode:executor", "prompt_version": "P0_writer_pdf_v1.5", "ts": "2026-04-28T00:00:00Z"}}
